:Description: trimmed input for use with Alquimia interface to Amanzi
:             for tritium decay

:=========================== chemistry ========================================
CHEMISTRY
  PRIMARY_SPECIES
    Tritium
  /
  GENERAL_REACTION
    REACTION Tritium <-> 
    FORWARD_RATE 1.78577E-09 ! t_1/2 = 12.32 years
    BACKWARD_RATE 0.d0
  /
  DATABASE ./tritium.dat
  LOG_FORMULATION
  ACTIVITY_COEFFICIENTS OFF
  OUTPUT
    All
    TOTAL
  /
  MAX_RESIDUAL_TOLERANCE 1.d-40
END

:=========================== constraints ======================================
CONSTRAINT initial
  CONCENTRATIONS
    Tritium  1.0e-20    T
  /
END

CONSTRAINT west
  CONCENTRATIONS
    Tritium  1.d-3      T
  /
END

CONSTRAINT westhi
  CONCENTRATIONS
    Tritium  1.d-2      T
  /
END

CONSTRAINT east
  CONCENTRATIONS
    Tritium  1.d-15      T
  /
END
